title: Sunset Edge. Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD] (2015)
description:
In theaters: May 29th, 2015

Description:

Deep in the woods, a graveyard of abandoned trailers sit rotting on a dead-end road. Welcome to Sunset Edge. When four suburban teens show up to hang out, they have no idea a shadow moves among them... a trickster tormented by a horrific past. Darkness falls, people disappear, and the secrets of Sunset Edge are revealed in a haunting finale.

Director: Daniel Peddle

Writers: Daniel Peddle

Actors: Gilberto Padilla, Jacob Ingle, Haley McKnight, William Dickerson, Blaine Pugh, Jack Horn, Liliane Gillenwater, Alex Padilla-Maya, Andy Foltz, Camilla Bueno

Genre: Thriller

Run Time: 1 hour 27 minutes
